      "acceptanceCriteria": "Manufactured solution or benchmark comparison demonstrating solver correctness for rotating-frame Navier-Stokes and scalar transport relevant to hemolysis power-law model.",
      "rationale": "Code verification performed against Taylor-Couette benchmark and FDA nozzle benchmark (FDA CFD round-robin). Observed order of accuracy consistent with nominal second-order scheme. No anomalous convergence behavior detected."
