      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) < 5% for hemolysis index QoI across at least three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study conducted at the nominal operating point (5 L/min, 2400 RPM). GCI for relative hemolysis index was 2.8%. Medium mesh (4.2M elements) selected for production runs as it achieved the required accuracy with acceptable computational cost."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
